<a class="lemma-anchor para-title" name="1"></a>
<a class="lemma-anchor" name="sub78591_1"></a>
<a class="lemma-anchor" name="地理环境"></a>
</div><div class="para-title level-2" label-module="para-title">
<h2 class="title-text"><span class="title-prefix">玉渡山风景区</span>地理环境</h2>
<a class="edit-icon j-edit-link" data-edit-dl="1" href="javascript:;"><em class="cmn-icon wiki-lemma-icons wiki-lemma-icons_edit-lemma"></em>编辑</a>
</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para"><a href="/item/%E7%8E%89%E6%B8%A1%E5%B1%B1" target="_blank">玉渡山</a>风景区位于北京市<a href="/item/%E5%BB%B6%E5%BA%86%E5%8E%BF" target="_blank">延庆县</a>城西北山中的玉渡山<div class="lemma-picture text-pic layout-right" style="width:220px; float: right;">
<a class="image-link" href="/pic/%E7%8E%89%E6%B8%A1%E5%B1%B1%E9%A3%8E%E6%99%AF%E5%8C%BA/1420186/0/a54e55fb76b6fa4e034f56a2?fr=lemma&amp;ct=single" nslog-type="9317" style="width:220px;height:144px;" target="_blank" title="玉渡山石灰岩峡谷">
<img alt="玉渡山石灰岩峡谷" class="lazy-img" data-src="https://gss1.bdstatic.com/-vo3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/s%3D220/sign=9483ed14b13533faf1b6942c98d3fdca/b7fd5266d01609242643c601d40735fae6cd3441.jpg" src="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAMAAAAoyzS7AAAAGXRFWHRTb2Z0d2FyZQBBZG9iZSBJbWFnZVJlYWR5ccllPAAAAAZQTFRF9fX1AAAA0VQI3QAAAAxJREFUeNpiYAAIMAAAAgABT21Z4QAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==" style="width:220px;height:144px;"/>
</a>
<span class="description">
玉渡山石灰岩峡谷
</span>
</div><a href="/item/%E8%87%AA%E7%84%B6%E9%A3%8E%E6%99%AF%E5%8C%BA" target="_blank">自然风景区</a>,全境面积约一百多平方公里,自<a href="/item/110%E5%9B%BD%E9%81%93" target="_blank">110国道</a>,有一条玉海公路相通。该区地处深山，人迹罕至，景色秀丽，环境清幽。它是北京地区一块鲜为人知的处女地；它是大自然保存最原始的绿色记忆；它是现代人回归自然最美好的选择。它是藏于深山的明珠，与我们现代人有着同样的渴望，这就是“天人合一”的至高境界。</div><div class="anchor-list">
<a class="lemma-anchor para-title" name="2"></a>
<a class="lemma-anchor" name="sub78591_2"></a>
<a class="lemma-anchor" name="主要景点"></a>
</div><div class="para-title level-2" label-module="para-title">
<h2 class="title-text"><span class="title-prefix">玉渡山风景区</span>主要景点</h2>
<a class="edit-icon j-edit-link" data-edit-dl="2" href="javascript:;"><em class="cmn-icon wiki-lemma-icons wiki-lemma-icons_edit-lemma"></em>编辑</a>
</div>
<div class="anchor-list">
<a class="lemma-anchor para-title" name="2_1"></a>
<a class="lemma-anchor" name="sub78591_2_1"></a>
<a class="lemma-anchor" name="玉渡山"></a>
<a class="lemma-anchor" name="2-1"></a>
</div><div class="para-title level-3" label-module="para-title">
<h3 class="title-text"><span class="title-prefix">玉渡山风景区</span>玉渡山</h3>
</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">玉渡山又称“一垛山”，是一座净高不过20米的离堆山，海拔860米，<a class="lemma-album layout-right nslog:10000206" href="/pic/%E7%8E%89%E6%B8%A1%E5%B1%B1%E9%A3%8E%E6%99%AF%E5%8C%BA/1420186/23655009/0df3d7ca7bcb0a463afcd1fb6763f6246a60af12?fr=lemma&amp;ct=cover" nslog-type="10000206" style="width:222px;" target="_blank" title="玉渡山风景区">
<div class="album-wrap" style="width:220px;height:165px;">
<img alt="玉渡山风景区" class="picture" src="https://gss0.bdstatic.com/94o3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/s%3D220/sign=4337dcee8b01a18bf4eb154dae2d0761/0df3d7ca7bcb0a463afcd1fb6763f6246a60af12.jpg" style="width:220px;height:165px;"/>
</div>
<div class="description">
玉渡山风景区<span class="number">(3张)</span>
</div>
<div class="albumBg">
<div class="albumBgFir" style="width:214px;"></div>
<div class="albumBgSec" style="width:208px;"></div>
</div>
</a>
山顶平整，长满灌丛，山顶长不过20米，宽7.8米，岩石均为砾岩，山虽然不高但极陡，如平地拔起，山顶原有一座小庙，名“<a href="/item/%E7%8E%89%E7%9A%87%E5%BA%99" target="_blank">玉皇庙</a>”，现庙已毁，只留墙基，断砖残迹。玉渡山周围郁郁葱葱，是一片绿的世界。植被极好，山下溪水四季不断流，严冬不冻。这里的古油松是较突出的，山顶山门遗址旁有一古松挺立，高20多米，直径近一米，<a href="/item/%E5%B1%B1%E5%8D%97" target="_blank">山南</a>峭壁又有一树身外探的古松，树冠青葱繁茂，与前一棵分别为<a href="/item/%E8%BF%8E%E5%AE%A2%E6%9D%BE" target="_blank">迎客松</a>和送客松。玉渡山对面山坡（正对山门，相隔100米）有三棵等距而立的古松，笔直挺立，人称“<a href="/item/%E4%B8%89%E7%82%B7%E9%A6%99" target="_blank">三炷香</a>”。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">因为水文条件好,人为活动少，封闭性强，所以这一地区植物生长茂盛，种类繁多。据<a href="/item/%E9%A6%96%E9%83%BD%E5%B8%88%E8%8C%83%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%A6" target="_blank">首都师范大学</a>和林业大学调查,乔木主要由松、桦、山杨、<div class="lemma-picture text-pic layout-right" style="width:220px; float: right;">
<a class="image-link" href="/pic/%E7%8E%89%E6%B8%A1%E5%B1%B1%E9%A3%8E%E6%99%AF%E5%8C%BA/1420186/0/6398ecd3966140f5a9ec9add?fr=lemma&amp;ct=single" nslog-type="9317" style="width:220px;height:165px;" target="_blank" title="玉渡山">
<img alt="玉渡山" class="lazy-img" data-src="https://gss1.bdstatic.com/9vo3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/s%3D220/sign=5666852d35fae6cd08b4ac633fb30f9e/4bed2e738bd4b31c464cf0a187d6277f9e2ff8bc.jpg" src="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAMAAAAoyzS7AAAAGXRFWHRTb2Z0d2FyZQBBZG9iZSBJbWFnZVJlYWR5ccllPAAAAAZQTFRF9fX1AAAA0VQI3QAAAAxJREFUeNpiYAAIMAAAAgABT21Z4QAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==" style="width:220px;height:165px;"/>
</a>
<span class="description">
玉渡山
</span>
</div>辽东栎、椴和<a href="/item/%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E4%B8%81%E9%A6%99" target="_blank">北京丁香</a>为主的沟谷杂本林组成；灌林木主要以山榆、二色胡枝子、<a href="/item/%E5%B9%B3%E6%A6%9B" target="_blank">平榛</a>、虎榛、绣线菊、鼠李、山桃、荆条、山杏等组成,草本主要为百草群落，部分荆条、灌丛相结合,这里植被覆盖度高（<a href="/item/%E7%8E%89%E6%B8%A1%E5%B1%B1" target="_blank">玉渡山</a>周围可达 100%），种类多，生长好，是天然的北方植物园。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">玉渡山之美,在于山、石、林、泉、瀑、花、草一应俱全、而那浑如天籁的感觉，又在于清、幽、静、野之中。溪中大小卵石磨圆较好，春、夏、秋三季花开不断，山清水秀,，鸟语花香，是山、水、林绝妙配合的静谷风光。<sup class="sup--normal" data-ctrmap=":2," data-sup="2">
[2]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_[2]_78591"> </a>
</div><div class="anchor-list">
<a class="lemma-anchor para-title" name="2_2"></a>
<a class="lemma-anchor" name="sub78591_2_2"></a>
<a class="lemma-anchor" name="石佛寺"></a>
<a class="lemma-anchor" name="2-2"></a>
</div><div class="para-title level-3" label-module="para-title">
<h3 class="title-text"><span class="title-prefix">玉渡山风景区</span>石佛寺</h3>
</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para" style="clear: both;"><a href="/item/%E7%9F%B3%E4%BD%9B%E5%AF%BA" target="_blank">石佛寺</a>景区有飞流直下的“海坨飞瀑”和白干绿盖的桦树林，有“天外飞石”的龙门口等诸多雄奇秀野的绚丽风景。</div><div class="anchor-list">
<a class="lemma-anchor para-title" name="2_3"></a>
<a class="lemma-anchor" name="sub78591_2_3"></a>
<a class="lemma-anchor" name="双松寺"></a>
<a class="lemma-anchor" name="2-3"></a>
</div><div class="para-title level-3" label-module="para-title">
<h3 class="title-text"><span class="title-prefix">玉渡山风景区</span>双松寺</h3>
</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para"><div class="lemma-picture text-pic layout-right" style="width:220px; float: right;">
<a class="image-link" href="/pic/%E7%8E%89%E6%B8%A1%E5%B1%B1%E9%A3%8E%E6%99%AF%E5%8C%BA/1420186/0/cdbf6c81800a19d832fea91235fa828ba61e4623?fr=lemma&amp;ct=single" nslog-type="9317" style="width:220px;height:146px;" target="_blank" title="">
<img alt="" class="lazy-img" data-src="https://gss2.bdstatic.com/-fo3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/s%3D220/sign=03d019ce3f01213fcb3349de64e636f8/cdbf6c81800a19d832fea91235fa828ba61e4623.jpg" src="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAMAAAAoyzS7AAAAGXRFWHRTb2Z0d2FyZQBBZG9iZSBJbWFnZVJlYWR5ccllPAAAAAZQTFRF9fX1AAAA0VQI3QAAAAxJREFUeNpiYAAIMAAAAgABT21Z4QAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==" style="width:220px;height:146px;"/>
</a>
</div>双松寺遗址始建于明代，清朝年间重建，由于此寺北靠<a href="/item/%E9%9D%92%E9%BE%99%E5%B1%B1" target="_blank">青龙山</a>，院内有两棵松，故名“青龙山双松寺”。双松寺遗址对面有一陡峭的金字塔形山，山势雄伟，山顶有直立的石锥，颇为壮观；双松寺南有一座“茶壶山”，夏天，在山谷中向山上远望，在雾气蒙蒙之中，其秀丽颇似南方山峦；更有那<a href="/item/%E4%BA%94%E9%87%8C%E5%9D%A1%E6%9D%91" target="_blank">五里坡村</a>的丁香沟和晶体透明的白色石英，其观赏价值极高。</div><div class="anchor-list">
<a class="lemma-anchor para-title" name="2_4"></a>
<a class="lemma-anchor" name="sub78591_2_4"></a>
<a class="lemma-anchor" name="二龙山"></a>
<a class="lemma-anchor" name="2-4"></a>
</div><div class="para-title level-3" label-module="para-title">
<h3 class="title-text"><span class="title-prefix">玉渡山风景区</span>二龙山</h3>
</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para"><a href="/item/%E4%BA%8C%E9%BE%99%E5%B1%B1" target="_blank">二龙山</a>是两个孤立的山峰，十分陡峭，远望好似两条龙头，故此得名，谷底有一“石门”，高约10米左右<a class="lemma-album layout-right nslog:10000206" href="/pic/%E7%8E%89%E6%B8%A1%E5%B1%B1%E9%A3%8E%E6%99%AF%E5%8C%BA/1420186/2598072/b58f8c5494eef01f9c19c230e0fe9925bc317d32?fr=lemma&amp;ct=cover" nslog-type="10000206" style="width:222px;" target="_blank" title="玉渡山风景区">
<div class="album-wrap" style="width:220px;height:146px;">
<img alt="玉渡山风景区" class="picture" src="https://gss2.bdstatic.com/-fo3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/s%3D220/sign=5dc25dd49313b07eb9bd570a3cd69113/b58f8c5494eef01f9c19c230e0fe9925bc317d32.jpg" style="width:220px;height:146px;"/>
</div>
<div class="description">
玉渡山风景区<span class="number">(6张)</span>
</div>
<div class="albumBg">
<div class="albumBgFir" style="width:214px;"></div>
<div class="albumBgSec" style="width:208px;"></div>
</div>
</a>
，两侧笔直，山坡上植被茂密，主要有青杠、狼榆、辽东栋、样树、六道木、胡枝子和棒子等。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">这里还有一条石灰岩峡谷，游人可沿河流顺谷而下至<a href="/item/%E9%BE%99%E5%BA%86%E5%B3%A1" target="_blank">龙庆峡</a>。这段峡谷长约10公里，谷底狭窄，两侧山峰陡峭，遍布峰林、峰丛、孤峰、石锥，缓坡和台地上，次生林茂密，景色十分秀丽迷人。</div><div class="anchor-list">
<a class="lemma-anchor para-title" name="3"></a>
<a class="lemma-anchor" name="sub78591_3"></a>
<a class="lemma-anchor" name="旅游信息"></a>
</div><div class="para-title level-2" label-module="para-title">
<h2 class="title-text"><span class="title-prefix">玉渡山风景区</span>旅游信息</h2>
<a class="edit-icon j-edit-link" data-edit-dl="3" href="javascript:;"><em class="cmn-icon wiki-lemma-icons wiki-lemma-icons_edit-lemma"></em>编辑</a>
</div>
<div class="anchor-list">
<a class="lemma-anchor para-title" name="3_1"></a>
<a class="lemma-anchor" name="sub78591_3_1"></a>
<a class="lemma-anchor" name="外部交通"></a>
<a class="lemma-anchor" name="3-1"></a>
</div><div class="para-title level-3" label-module="para-title">
<h3 class="title-text"><span class="title-prefix">玉渡山风景区</span>外部交通</h3>
</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para"><b></b><b>自驾</b><br/>　　沿八达岭高速路行驶，<a data-lemmaid="128981" href="/item/%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC/128981" target="_blank">北京</a>到<a href="/item/%E9%BE%99%E5%BA%86%E5%B3%A1" target="_blank">龙庆峡</a>（玉渡山）约70分钟。</div><div class="anchor-list">
<a class="lemma-anchor para-title" name="3_2"></a>
<a class="lemma-anchor" name="sub78591_3_2"></a>
<a class="lemma-anchor" name="内部交通"></a>
<a class="lemma-anchor" name="3-2"></a>
</div><div class="para-title level-3" label-module="para-title">
<h3 class="title-text"><span class="title-prefix">玉渡山风景区</span>内部交通</h3>
</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para"><b>公共交通</b><br/>　　1、游8路（旅游专线车）始发站：前门、安定门地铁西口（每周六、日发车），在龙庆峡站下车。<br/>　　2、919路（市郊车）始发站：德胜门箭楼每5分钟对开一辆，到延庆县城再乘920环线到龙庆峡（玉渡山）。</div><div class="anchor-list">
<a class="lemma-anchor para-title" name="3_3"></a>
<a class="lemma-anchor" name="sub78591_3_3"></a>
<a class="lemma-anchor" name="门票价格"></a>
<a class="lemma-anchor" name="3-3"></a>
</div><div class="para-title level-3" label-module="para-title">
<h3 class="title-text"><span class="title-prefix">玉渡山风景区</span>门票价格</h3>
</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para"><b>门票价格：</b>60元</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">其他优惠 ：身高1.2米（含1.2米）至1.5米（含1.5米）的儿童，65周岁至69周岁的长者（凭有效身份证验票入园）门票30元；1.2米以下免费；70岁以上的老人免费。残疾人免费。<sup class="sup--normal" data-ctrmap=":3," data-sup="3">
[3]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_[3]_78591"> </a>
<a class="lemma-album layout-right nslog:10000206" href="/pic/%E7%8E%89%E6%B8%A1%E5%B1%B1%E9%A3%8E%E6%99%AF%E5%8C%BA/1420186/21529961/d50735fae6cd7b895c611663062442a7d8330ec4?fr=lemma&amp;ct=cover" nslog-type="10000206" style="width:222px;" target="_blank" title="玉渡山风景区">
<div class="album-wrap" style="width:220px;height:110px;">
<img alt="玉渡山风景区" class="picture" src="https://gss2.bdstatic.com/9fo3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/s%3D220/sign=6ae3e4cf4834970a4373172da5cbd1c0/d50735fae6cd7b895c611663062442a7d8330ec4.jpg" style="width:220px;height:110px;"/>
</div>
<div class="description">
玉渡山风景区<span class="number">(6张)</span>
